			<ns0:name>elijahtaylor@google.com</ns0:name><ns0:uri>/u/elijahtaylor@google.com/</ns0:uri></ns0:author><ns0:content type="html">The PDF scrollbar doesn't handle resize events correctly

Steps:
1) Load a PDF with enough vertical space to require a scrollbar
2) Save the pdf using the built-in save icon
3) When the download bar comes up, notice the scrollbar turns black until you hover over it or scroll the page

Alternate:
1) Load a PDF
2) resize the window smaller until scrollbars are needed (horizontal or vertical)
